fields.name: How To!
fields.value:
**1:** Go to your profile [Click Here](https://younow.com/${slashParams("younowUsername")})
**2:** Remove everything currently on your profile.
**3:** Place the code below and save your profile.
__Give YouNow Api about 1 min to update__
**4:** use `!link` in any server this bot is in.
**Enjoy the benifits of a linked account.**
